{"tid":1602733,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【唔好再講良心 係人性】畜牲圍毆手足後散水","createTime":"2019-09-29T13:31:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T20:51:01.000Z","uid":228437,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0c447e5d2135205e462c957c4292f50770205bb2","tid":1602733,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:31:42.000Z","msg":"香港人，唔該唔撚好幻想有白警啦<br />\n條片好撚明顯，啡色鞋果啲速龍係武警（一早證實左）<br />\n拉個手足果啲畜牲入面得一個武警<br />\n其他全部雜差狗黎，個撚個係咁吽，<br />\n有一個仲桶落去，吽撚完就散水，由得啲啡鞋執手尾，睇真啲反而個武警仲有返下佢個頭<br />\n<br />\n你班畜牲唔撚好諗住乜撚屈落武警度<br />\n就算真係有武警做，你地都要全部啃左佢！<br />\n邊撚個叫你地咁撚死蠢唔Show號碼呀<br />\n<br />\n唔該大家唔好再問佢地良心去左邊，良心已經高撚左一級！大家唔該係要問佢地<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">人性去撚左邊！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家跟我講一次：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人&middot;性&middot;去&middot;左&middot;邊？！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V4LjUMo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV4LjUMo.png&h=ce1394d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bv0WWZK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBv0WWZK.png&h=1f0a5a02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來源：理大編委<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/305868249479813/posts/2494125477320735?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F305868249479813%2Fposts%2F2494125477320735%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLTYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=ecb15ef6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/305868249479813/posts/2494125477320735?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"fe9b617389ba460a33da44a9997cea7fdadd922d","tid":1602733,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:31:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"acc1b92a767d1b201b9c550a3cf02da6d54cdd32","tid":1602733,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-